OL,3,CMan and woman arrested over Lisa
OL,4,CDorrian disappearance released
OL,6,FA man and a woman arrested by
OL,7,Fdetectives investigating the
OL,8,Fdisappearance and presumed murder of
OL,9,FLisa Dorrian have been released.
OL,11,FThe 25-year-old from Bangor, Co Down,
OL,12,Fwas last seen alive on 27 February
OL,13,F2005 after attending a party at
OL,14,FBallyhalbert Caravan Park.
OL,16,FDespite extensive searches in multiple
OL,17,Flocations and campaigning by her
OL,18,Ffamily, Ms Dorrian's body has never
OL,19,Fbeen found.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
