OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772216417
OL,3,CMan and woman arrested over Lisa
OL,4,CDorrian disappearance released
OL,6,FPolice believe Lisa was murdered on
OL,7,Fthe night of February 27 or in the
OL,8,Fearly hours of the following morning.
OL,10,FA 40-year-old woman was arrested in
OL,11,FBangor on Wednesday, and later a 42-
OL,12,Fyear-old man was arrested in Scotland.
OL,14,FThey were both arrested on suspicion
OL,15,Fof murder, assisting offenders,
OL,16,Fwithholding information and preventing
OL,17,Fa lawful and decent burial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
