OL,3,CMan and woman arrested over Lisa
OL,4,CDorrian disappearance released
OL,6,FOn Thursday evening, the Police
OL,7,FService of Northern Ireland said both
OL,8,Fhad been released on bail pending
OL,9,Ffurther inquiries.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the PSNI said
OL,12,Fdetectives "remain determined to
OL,13,Fprovide justice for Lisa's family".
OL,15,FThey have appealed to anyone with
OL,16,Finformation about her disappearance
OL,17,Fand murder to contact them on 101.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
